{
  "stem": "14613.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was-- how should I say, created, or ordered by the leader of the Jews, which we called the eldest [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- he was really a very caring person before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he cared for children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He volunteered to work-- he worked in orphanage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore, in ghetto, when he came, one of his first thing was to see what to do with and for the children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- and he made for us, the children, a school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was pretty far from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at the beginning, we used to go to this school, which was on [NON-ENGLISH], which was a different part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But like everything else, it got worse and worse, and the school was closed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's when our father started to take a private tutor to teach so that we wouldn't lose the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But even that had to stop after a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And slowly, what you can call the screw tightened, and we can see that it gets from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People were getting very small ration of food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that they used to make [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] what they call resorts that people had to work there for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The people that did not work, did not get any ration.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you could see, really, from day to day, the starvation which took place in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- in a very poor section of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the war, I never went there to this section.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it's not-- I didn't know much about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was in a poor section of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And like I say, the situation was very bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The starvation was pronounced from day to day.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
